OL,3,CNew dispute over car loans scandal
OL,4,Cpayouts
OL,6,FThe trade body which represents the
OL,7,Fmotor finance sector says it will
OL,8,Foppose current plans for a payout
OL,9,Fscheme to those who were unfairly sold
OL,10,Fcar finance, in a significant
OL,11,Fdevelopment in the scandal.
OL,13,FThe redress scheme, proposed by the
OL,14,FFinancial Conduct Authority (FCA),
OL,15,Faims to compensate motorists who were
OL,16,Funfairly sold a car loan between 2007
OL,17,Fand 2024 because they were not
OL,18,Fproperly informed about the commission
OL,19,Fpaid to brokers, including car dealers.
