OL,6,FAround 14 million deals could be
OL,7,Feligible for hundreds of pounds
OL,8,Fthrough the scheme.
OL,10,FHowever, the Finance and Leasing
OL,11,FAssociation (FLA), has now said:
OL,12,F"While lenders fully support a robust
OL,13,Fand credible redress programme for
OL,14,Fcustomers who have suffered loss, the
OL,15,FFLA warns that the scheme as drafted
OL,16,Fcannot deliver the fairness,
OL,17,Fsimplicity, finality, efficiency or
OL,18,Fcertainty the FCA set out as its own
OL,19,Fguiding principles."
