OL,11,FThe FCA also intervened in the case,
OL,12,Ftelling the UK's highest court that
OL,13,Fthe Court of Appeal ruling "goes too
OL,14,Ffar", while the three motorists
OL,15,Fopposed the challenge.
OL,17,FIn August, the Supreme Court ruled
OL,18,Fthat lenders are not liable for hidden
OL,19,Fcommission payments in car finance
OL,20,Fschemes, meaning millions could miss
OL,21,Fout on compensation.
