OL,6,FThe FCA then set out proposals for an
OL,7,Findustry-wide scheme to compensate
OL,8,Fmotorists.
OL,10,FIt is currently consulting on the
OL,11,Fdetails of the scheme, which is
OL,12,Fexpected to launch early next year.
OL,14,FThe watchdog says said its free scheme
OL,15,Fis the quickest and simplest way for
OL,16,Fconsumers to access compensation and
OL,17,Ffor lenders to administer payouts.
